 evaluation of the hierarchical trees to obtain optimal partitions;\nand, 4) Outputs compatible with popular software such as MEGA and Cytoscape.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Apr 2012 11:16:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Dec 2012 15:15:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 19 Dec 2012 10:11:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-20"}
