itude, if confirmed by future studies, highlights that molecules are\nmissing in Virgo HI deficient spirals, but to a somewhat lesser extent than\ndust.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Apr 2012 13:42:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
