onized component is always similar to the disk one,\nwhich confirms that the ultra-soft state (seen in other brighter black hole\nsystems) is not exhibited by Cyg X-1. The rapid variation of the Compton\nAmplification factor with $\\Gamma$, naturally explains the absence of spectra\nwith $\\Gamma < 1.6$, despite a large number having $\\Gamma \\sim 1.65$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Apr 2012 13:52:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
